---
// src/components/Hero.astro
// Красивый Hero-блок в стиле Ethera
---

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-20">
  <div
    class="glass-card shine-border rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-14 max-w-4xl w-full relative overflow-hidden group"
  >
    <!-- Эффект свечения при ховере -->
    <div
      class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-primary)] via-purple-500 to-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-3xl blur-xl opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-30 transition-all duration-1000"
    >
    </div>

    <!-- Верхняя граница-блик -->
    <div
      class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/30 to-transparent"
    >
    </div>

    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col gap-8">
      <!-- Статус badge -->
      <div class="scroll-animate">
        <div
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)]/10 border border-[var(--color-primary)]/20 w-fit"
        >
          <span class="relative flex h-2.5 w-2.5">
            <span
              class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[var(--color-primary)] opacity-75"
            ></span>
            <span
              class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2.5 w-2.5 bg-[var(--color-primary)]"
            ></span>
          </span>
          <span
            class="text-[var(--color-primary)] text-xs font-semibold tracking-wider uppercase"
          >
            <span class="lang-ru">Открыт к предложениям</span>
            <span class="lang-en">Available for work</span>
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Заголовок -->
      <div class="scroll-animate" style="transition-delay: 100ms;">
        <h1
          class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight font-cinzel"
        >
          <span class="lang-ru">
            Привет, я
            <span class="text-gradient">Ярослав</span>
          </span>
          <span class="lang-en">
            Hi, I'm
            <span class="text-gradient">Yaroslav</span>
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p
          class="text-xl md:text-3xl text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] font-light mt-4"
        >
          <span class="lang-ru">Full-Stack Архитектор</span>
          <span class="lang-en">Full-Stack Architect</span>
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Описание -->
      <p
        class="scroll-animate text-base md:text-lg text-[var(--color-muted-foreground)] max-w-2xl leading-relaxed"
        style="transition-delay: 200ms;"
      >
        <span class="lang-ru"
          >Превращаю хаос в структуру, а идеи — в цифровое искусство.
          Специализируюсь на создании высокопроизводительных веб-систем,
          Telegram-ботов и десктоп-приложений.</span
        >
        <span class="lang-en"
          >Turning chaos into structure and ideas into digital art. Specializing
          in high-performance web systems, Telegram bots, and desktop
          applications.</span
        >
      </p>

      <!-- Кнопки -->
      <div
        class="scroll-animate flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-4"
        style="transition-delay: 300ms;"
      >
        <a
          href="#projects"
          class="btn-primary inline-flex items-center gap-2 group/btn"
        >
          <span class="lang-ru">Смотреть проекты</span>
          <span class="lang-en">View Projects</span>
          <svg
            class="w-5 h-5 transition-transform group-hover/btn:translate-x-1"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          >
            <path
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
              stroke-width="2"
              d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"></path>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-secondary inline-flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="lang-ru">Обо мне</span>
          <span class="lang-en">About Me</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Стек технологий -->
      <div
        class="scroll-animate mt-8 pt-8 border-t border-[var(--color-border)]"
        style="transition-delay: 400ms;"
      >
        <p class="section-title mb-4">
          <span class="lang-ru">Технологии</span>
          <span class="lang-en">Tech Stack</span>
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          {
            [
              "Python",
              "TypeScript",
              "C#",
              "Next.js",
              "Astro",
              "Tailwind",
              "PostgreSQL",
              "Redis",
            ].map((tech) => <span class="tag">{tech}</span>)
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
